{"about_the_game":"In this cooperative roguelike action adventure game, choose a class and play with up to 4 players as ice cream dogs Neo, Coby, Chaz and Miley. Venture through the Savage Garden and ascend the Dark Tower to defeat the Calico King. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_01.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/store_ballpit.gif?t=1733958275\" /><br>Each run presents new puzzles, enemies, skills and items to discover. As you advance, the Tower and the King grow stronger, offering fresh challenges with every playthrough.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_02.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/store_fight.gif?t=1733958275\" /><br>Battle your way through hordes of enemies and bosses, each with their own set of unique attacks and abilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_03.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/store_clawshot.gif?t=1733958275\" /><br>Each class has their own unique set of skills and upgrades that vary from run to run. Try out different combinations to find the best build for your play style. Uncover the Tower's secrets unlock new powers to aid future runs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_04.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/store_slide.gif?t=1733958275\" /><br>Team up with up to four players. Work together to defeat enemies, solve puzzles, and play minigames.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733958275","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/page.bg.jpg?t=1733958275","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/80144b48cfef37ad0c03e7ba62433adafbdf5f96/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733958275","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/80144b48cfef37ad0c03e7ba62433adafbdf5f96/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733958275","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"In this cooperative roguelike action adventure game, choose a class and play with up to 4 players as ice cream dogs Neo, Coby, Chaz and Miley. Venture through the Savage Garden and ascend the Dark Tower to defeat the Calico King. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_01.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/store_ballpit.gif?t=1733958275\" /><br>Each run presents new puzzles, enemies, skills and items to discover. As you advance, the Tower and the King grow stronger, offering fresh challenges with every playthrough.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157380/extras/Banner_02.png?t=1733958275\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as